executeLater

public void executeLater(java.lang.Iterable<ISubjectObserver<ITaskResult<TResult>>> observers,
                         ObserverFailureHandlingMode observerFailureHandlingMode)
Executes this task in the background using another thread. Non-blocking method, returns immediately. The result is notified to all specified observers, one at a time (non-concurrently). Uses the specified observer notification failure to handle exceptions during observer notifications.
